attributes.description: Overview of Events logs in Cyera Integration.

params.markdown:
#### Cyera

#### Overview

This dashboard provides visibility into Events detected within Cyera, showing the total number of events along with breakdowns by type, report type, and data sensitivity. It highlights trends of events over time, top policies triggered, and key contributing users, domains, and vendors across cloud provider and SKUs. Additional panels surface report statuses, risk-associated issues, and datastore details, offering context that supports faster investigation, compliance monitoring, and effective remediation.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/cyera/overview)**
